title: Protect Your God-Sized Promises | Victoria Osteen
itunes:title: Protect Your God-Sized Promises | Victoria Osteen
description:
From the moment we were born, God gave us each an assignment. But we have to do our part and develop the gifts He’s given us. When you get into an environment where your gifts can grow, those seeds of promise will come to fruition. 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
